        <h2><br>Why mindfulness?</h2>
        <h3>And why for geeks?</h3>
        <p>Meditation practice has made a big difference for us, and we'd like to offer to share that with you.</p>
        <p>Everybody knows meditation can help with stress relief and has health benefits. But there are things we've found especially useful for us, as geeks. Mindfulness work has helped us with...</p>
        <ul>
          <li>becoming more comfortable with our emotions</li>
          <li>developing compassion</li>
          <li>achieving healthier focus</li>
          <li>control of our attention</li>
          <li>getting better at empathy</li>
          <li>gaining awareness of our bodies</li>
          <li>learning self-compassion</li>
          <li>improving relationships</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We'd like to invite you to join our six-week online class. Weekly group instruction and meditation sessions will happen via Hangouts, and throughout the course you'll have an online community for questions and thoughts that come to you between sessions. Together with a small group of other technical folks, you'll learn meditation basics and intermediate techniques, and begin to form habits that can stick with you.</p>
      <p><a href="#signup">Take me to sign up</a><span class="arrow"><a href="#signup">&#10164;</a></span></p>
      </div>
